1
00:00:09,012 --> 00:00:09,808
<i>C'mon!</i>

2
00:00:16,186 --> 00:00:18,814
<i>Running like a fugitive,</i>

3
00:00:19,856 --> 00:00:22,017
<i>Being chased by something</i>

4
00:00:23,693 --> 00:00:26,355
<i>Inside my heart is pounding</i>

5
00:00:27,464 --> 00:00:30,092
<i>My throat dry like it's withering</i>

6
00:00:31,801 --> 00:00:34,895
<i>For no single one,</i>

7
00:00:35,539 --> 00:00:38,667
<i>To none does belong,</i>

8
00:00:40,143 --> 00:00:44,512
<i>This time is ours, right now...</i>

9
00:00:47,150 --> 00:00:48,913
<i>Unraveling the pain,</i>

10
00:00:49,019 --> 00:00:50,748
<i>Unraveling our hearts,</i>

11
00:00:50,820 --> 00:00:53,152
<i>Unraveling shadows</i>

12
00:00:54,691 --> 00:00:56,454
<i>Stifling our breath,</i>

13
00:00:56,526 --> 00:00:58,426
<i>Reaching for beyond,</i>

14
00:00:58,495 --> 00:01:00,929
<i>Tearing through the dark</i>

15
00:01:02,832 --> 00:01:09,396
<i>In fighting and in love</i>

16
00:01:10,507 --> 00:01:12,998
<i>To the distant light above,</i>

17
00:01:13,777 --> 00:01:16,644
<i>Yes, we are on the way</i>

18
00:01:21,484 --> 00:01:22,781
<i>I wanna rock...</i>

19
00:01:25,255 --> 00:01:26,779
<i>Rockin' my heart</i>

20
00:01:35,009 --> 00:01:36,977
You're an embarrassment
to our village.

21
00:01:37,578 --> 00:01:40,570
Why do you think we came all
the way here to Leaf Village!?

22
00:01:40,647 --> 00:01:42,638
P-Please listen to me, Gaara.

23
00:01:43,851 --> 00:01:46,376
T-They lashed out first...

24
00:01:46,687 --> 00:01:47,551
Shut up!

25
00:01:50,824 --> 00:01:51,756
I'll kill you.

26
00:01:52,226 --> 00:01:55,423
U-Understood, I was wrong.

27
00:01:56,030 --> 00:01:58,055
I-I'm sorry...
I'm really sorry.

28
00:01:59,366 --> 00:02:01,834
I'm sorry about that...

29
00:02:02,836 --> 00:02:06,067
<i>This guy...has a nasty look.</i>

30
00:02:06,874 --> 00:02:08,865
<i>To think he was able to hit</i>
<i>that Kankuro</i>

31
00:02:08,942 --> 00:02:10,910
<i>with a tiny rock with great ease.</i>

32
00:02:11,578 --> 00:02:13,671
<i>This guy's...good.</i>

33
00:02:19,286 --> 00:02:20,082
Let's go.

34
00:02:20,487 --> 00:02:22,819
We didn't come here
to play around.

35
00:02:23,057 --> 00:02:24,422
I know.

36
00:02:25,025 --> 00:02:26,049
Hold it!

37
00:02:27,628 --> 00:02:28,356
What is it?

38
00:02:28,996 --> 00:02:30,293
Judging from your headbands,

39
00:02:30,364 --> 00:02:33,026
you're Ninjas from the Village
Hidden in the Sand, right?

40
00:02:34,768 --> 00:02:37,703
Without question, the Land of Fire and
the Land of Wind are allied nations.

41
00:02:37,905 --> 00:02:39,634
But the arbitrary coming and
going of Shinobi

42
00:02:39,706 --> 00:02:41,469
is supposed to
be prohibited by the treaty.

43
00:02:42,176 --> 00:02:43,473
State your purpose!

44
00:02:43,877 --> 00:02:45,037
Depending on circumstances...

45
00:02:45,112 --> 00:02:47,478
Hmph! So this is what they mean

46
00:02:47,548 --> 00:02:48,742
by the darkest place being
under the candlestick.

47
00:02:49,016 --> 00:02:50,449
Don't you know anything about it?

48
00:02:51,485 --> 00:02:52,611
My permit!

49
00:02:54,388 --> 00:02:58,950
As you say, we're Sand Village Genins
from the Land of Wind.

50
00:02:59,726 --> 00:03:02,627
We came to this village to
take the Chunin Exam.

51
00:03:03,497 --> 00:03:05,658
Chunin Exam...?

52
00:03:06,100 --> 00:03:11,936
<i>Identify Yourself.</i>
<i>Powerful New Rivals</i>

53
00:03:12,639 --> 00:03:15,802
What is the Chunin Exam anyways?

54
00:03:16,243 --> 00:03:18,268
You really don't know
anything, do you?

55
00:03:19,246 --> 00:03:24,343
Bro, if you pass the exam,
you can become a Chunin from a Genin!

56
00:03:24,718 --> 00:03:27,653
I see! Then, maybe I'll try taking them!

57
00:03:27,988 --> 00:03:28,511
Heh!

58
00:03:29,289 --> 00:03:31,723
Hey! You there...

59
00:03:32,326 --> 00:03:33,418
What's your name?

60
00:03:33,660 --> 00:03:35,355
Huh? M-Me?

61
00:03:35,829 --> 00:03:38,389
No! The gourd next to you!

62
00:03:40,834 --> 00:03:43,268
I'm Gaara of the desert...

63
00:03:43,904 --> 00:03:45,838
I have an interest in you as well...

64
00:03:46,573 --> 00:03:47,540
What's your name?

65
00:03:48,242 --> 00:03:50,039
Sasuke Uchiha.

66
00:03:57,451 --> 00:03:59,749
Say! Say! What about me?
What about me?

67
00:04:00,587 --> 00:04:01,679
Not interested.

68
00:04:05,592 --> 00:04:08,117
<i>Heh! Things have gotten interesting.</i>

69
00:04:09,663 --> 00:04:12,826
Konohamaru, do I look weak?

70
00:04:13,167 --> 00:04:15,601
Compared to Sasuke, yes...

71
00:04:17,838 --> 00:04:19,738
Sasuke, I won't lose to you!

72
00:04:19,806 --> 00:04:21,296
What's gotten into you,
all of a sudden?!

73
00:04:21,842 --> 00:04:22,866
What do you think?

74
00:04:23,377 --> 00:04:25,902
I don't think they're anything special.

75
00:04:26,380 --> 00:04:29,008
But the black-haired one from Leaf Village
and the gourd from the Sand Village...

76
00:04:29,283 --> 00:04:31,012
those two need to be checked.

77
00:04:33,053 --> 00:04:37,786
Now then, in conjunction
with beginning the Chunin Exam,

78
00:04:38,058 --> 00:04:42,154
let us first have those in charge
of the rookie Genin come forward.

79
00:04:43,764 --> 00:04:46,961
Kakashi and Kurenai and Asuma...

80
00:04:47,768 --> 00:04:50,828
So? Are there any Genin from
your squads

81
00:04:50,904 --> 00:04:54,533
you wish to recommend
for these exams?

82
00:04:55,776 --> 00:04:57,710
It goes without saying,

83
00:04:57,778 --> 00:05:02,078
but if it's a Genin who has carried out
eight or more formal missions,

84
00:05:02,149 --> 00:05:05,448
you can recommend them
for the exams if you wish.

85
00:05:05,986 --> 00:05:07,817
Well, as a general rule,

86
00:05:07,888 --> 00:05:11,949
having carried out more than twice
that amount of missions is appropriate.

87
00:05:12,392 --> 00:05:13,791
<i>There's no need to hear this...</i>

88
00:05:14,161 --> 00:05:16,026
<i>It's too soon for them.</i>

89
00:05:17,030 --> 00:05:18,588
Then, you first Kakashi.

90
00:05:19,833 --> 00:05:21,425
The Kakashi led Group Seven...

91
00:05:22,069 --> 00:05:26,597
Sasuke Uchiha. Naruto Uzumaki.
Sakura Haruno.

92
00:05:27,274 --> 00:05:33,338
I, Kakashi Hatake, recommend these
three for the Chunin Exam.

93
00:05:34,181 --> 00:05:34,704
Huh?

94
00:05:35,616 --> 00:05:37,447
The Kurenai led Group Eight...

95
00:05:37,618 --> 00:05:41,816
Hinata Hyuga, Kiba Inuzuka,
Shino Aburame.

96
00:05:42,222 --> 00:05:46,056
These three, I, Kurenai Yuhi,
recommend the same.

97
00:05:47,394 --> 00:05:49,157
The Asuma led Group Ten...

98
00:05:49,529 --> 00:05:54,091
Ino Yamanaka, Shikamaru Nara,
Choji Akimichi.

99
00:05:54,601 --> 00:05:58,697
These three, I, Asuma Sarutobi,
recommend the same.

100
00:05:59,106 --> 00:06:00,937
All three recommended...

101
00:06:01,008 --> 00:06:02,942
To think rookies will be
in the Chunin Exam...

102
00:06:03,010 --> 00:06:03,977
Hasn't it been five years
since that's happened?

103
00:06:05,479 --> 00:06:06,241
Hmm...

104
00:06:06,313 --> 00:06:07,644
Wait a minute!

105
00:06:08,148 --> 00:06:09,342
What is it, Iruka?

106
00:06:09,650 --> 00:06:11,982
Lord Hokage, please let me
say one thing.

107
00:06:12,486 --> 00:06:14,078
This may be presumptuous,

108
00:06:14,154 --> 00:06:16,384
but as for the nine names
that were given,

109
00:06:16,657 --> 00:06:18,625
I was in charge of them at the Academy.

110
00:06:19,493 --> 00:06:22,018
Admittedly, they were all students
with ability,

111
00:06:22,095 --> 00:06:23,426
but it's too soon...!

112
00:06:24,197 --> 00:06:27,325
They should be tested after
having gained more experience!

113
00:06:28,268 --> 00:06:32,796
I became a Chunin when I was
six years younger than Naruto is now.

114
00:06:33,006 --> 00:06:34,997
Naruto is different from you!

115
00:06:35,575 --> 00:06:37,566
Is it your intent to crush Naruto?!

116
00:06:38,278 --> 00:06:41,543
They always do nothing but complain
about important missions...

117
00:06:41,648 --> 00:06:44,549
Teaching them a lesson
once would be fun.

118
00:06:44,785 --> 00:06:46,980
Trying to crush them
would be interesting, too.

119
00:06:47,487 --> 00:06:48,977
W-What did you say?!

120
00:06:49,423 --> 00:06:51,914
Well, joking aside...

121
00:06:52,926 --> 00:06:54,086
Iruka Sensei...

122
00:06:55,195 --> 00:06:57,493
I understand what you want to say.

123
00:06:57,798 --> 00:07:00,266
It's aggravating, I know.
However...

124
00:07:00,534 --> 00:07:01,466
Kakashi...

125
00:07:01,535 --> 00:07:02,866
Don't do it.

126
00:07:03,804 --> 00:07:07,797
Stay out of this!
They're not your students anymore!

127
00:07:08,008 --> 00:07:10,806
Now they're my subordinates!

128
00:07:12,946 --> 00:07:15,915
<i>Man...troublesome people.</i>

129
00:07:20,887 --> 00:07:23,754
B-But the Chunin Exam
is also known as...

130
00:07:23,824 --> 00:07:24,688
Iruka...

131
00:07:25,659 --> 00:07:28,423
I understand your point.

132
00:07:29,262 --> 00:07:30,593
Master Hokage...

133
00:07:31,231 --> 00:07:33,825
Therefore, I have decided to conduct

134
00:07:33,900 --> 00:07:36,733
a special preliminary exam
for these rookie Genins.

135
00:07:37,237 --> 00:07:39,569
P-Preliminary exam?!

136
00:07:49,516 --> 00:07:50,676
Say! Say! Say!

137
00:07:50,951 --> 00:07:52,885
Why is it that he's the one who
always calls us out,

138
00:07:52,953 --> 00:07:54,386
and then makes us wait?!

139
00:07:54,554 --> 00:07:55,782
That's right! That's right!

140
00:07:56,156 --> 00:07:58,181
What's he going to do about
the feelings of a maiden

141
00:07:58,258 --> 00:08:00,988
who accidentally overslept and resigned
herself to no blow drying?!

142
00:08:01,194 --> 00:08:04,857
I overslept, so I haven't washed my face
and didn't brush my teeth.

143
00:08:06,066 --> 00:08:09,194
Y-You... That's dirty.

144
00:08:09,803 --> 00:08:13,398
<i>Why're these guys so hyper</i>
<i>first thing in the morning?!</i>

145
00:08:16,576 --> 00:08:18,601
Hey, good morning, folks!

146
00:08:19,079 --> 00:08:22,071
Today, I got a bit lost on the path of life...

147
00:08:22,249 --> 00:08:23,648
Right! That's a lie!!

148
00:08:25,519 --> 00:08:26,543
Uh, well...

149
00:08:26,620 --> 00:08:30,954
This is sudden, but I recommended
you guys for the Chunin Exam, so...

150
00:08:31,391 --> 00:08:33,018
Here, these are your applications.

151
00:08:33,527 --> 00:08:34,892
Chunin Exam...

152
00:08:35,662 --> 00:08:38,290
That being said, the recommendations
are not compulsory.

153
00:08:38,565 --> 00:08:41,966
You guys are free to decide whether
you take the Exam or not.

154
00:08:42,169 --> 00:08:44,967
All right! I love you, Kakashi Sensei!

155
00:08:45,038 --> 00:08:46,767
Hey, cut it out. Get away already...

156
00:08:47,407 --> 00:08:50,706
Only those who want to take the Exam,
sign that application and

157
00:08:50,777 --> 00:08:55,077
come to Room 301 of the Academy
at 3:00 p.m. Five days from now...

158
00:08:55,348 --> 00:08:56,212
That's it!

159
00:08:58,518 --> 00:09:00,884
Chunin Exam! Chunin Exam!

160
00:09:06,126 --> 00:09:08,026
Chunin Exams, eh...

161
00:09:08,829 --> 00:09:11,696
I bet lots of strong guys would be there...

162
00:09:12,599 --> 00:09:14,328
<i>For example, that guy!</i>

163
00:09:16,136 --> 00:09:17,626
<i>And this guy!</i>

164
00:09:22,976 --> 00:09:27,413
Okaaay! I won't lose to
anybody no matter what!

165
00:09:28,748 --> 00:09:32,741
If I take the first place, the path to
the Hokage is right there!

166
00:09:33,153 --> 00:09:37,112
<i>Sure enough, it's decided that Naruto</i>
<i>will be the Hokage...</i>

167
00:09:37,190 --> 00:09:39,750
<i>I'll just retire my elderly self at once.</i>

168
00:09:39,826 --> 00:09:40,815
<i>Yaaaay!</i>

169
00:09:44,231 --> 00:09:46,096
<i>I might be able to fight him.</i>

170
00:09:54,574 --> 00:09:55,802
<i>I...don't want to...</i>

171
00:09:57,811 --> 00:09:58,869
<i>Here I can't...</i>

172
00:09:59,279 --> 00:10:01,474
<i>keep up with Sasuke,</i>
<i>and not even with Naruto...</i>

173
00:10:01,548 --> 00:10:03,175
<i>The Chunin Exam, no way...</i>

174
00:10:26,573 --> 00:10:29,940
Oh, Brother Naruto! Let's play!

175
00:10:30,010 --> 00:10:34,344
Sure. I don't have any missions today,
so I'll play with you guys!

176
00:10:34,548 --> 00:10:36,038
Yaaay!

177
00:10:37,083 --> 00:10:37,674
Oh!

178
00:10:43,223 --> 00:10:46,249
Leader! Konohamaru!

179
00:10:46,326 --> 00:10:48,590
What're you going to do with Moegi?!

180
00:10:48,662 --> 00:10:50,630
Hey, you! Let Moegi go!

181
00:10:54,200 --> 00:10:56,430
Darn!
Let's follow them, Konohamaru!

182
00:10:56,603 --> 00:10:57,797
Y-Yeah!

183
00:10:58,171 --> 00:10:59,160
W-Wait!

184
00:11:10,017 --> 00:11:12,679
Chunin Exams, eh...

185
00:11:13,687 --> 00:11:14,415
Yo.

186
00:11:14,789 --> 00:11:17,417
S-Sasuke, what's up?

187
00:11:18,025 --> 00:11:19,856
How about we go for a little walk?

188
00:11:20,461 --> 00:11:22,827
No way! For real?!

189
00:11:25,866 --> 00:11:28,926
<i>Well well... So you can keep up</i>
<i>at this speed, eh?</i>

190
00:11:30,104 --> 00:11:32,163
Wait for me! Moegi!

191
00:11:36,043 --> 00:11:38,204
Bro, where'd you go?

192
00:11:38,612 --> 00:11:40,409
I think we are lost.

193
00:11:40,781 --> 00:11:42,373
Nooo! Let me go!

194
00:11:44,752 --> 00:11:47,050
Even the strongly fortified
Village Hidden in the Leaf...

195
00:11:47,588 --> 00:11:51,046
is mine if I slip in the
middle of Chunin Exam's ruckus.

196
00:11:51,458 --> 00:11:52,288
Hmm?

197
00:11:53,160 --> 00:11:54,252
That was fast...

198
00:11:54,929 --> 00:11:56,726
Hey! You fat old man!

199
00:11:56,864 --> 00:11:58,832
What're you going to do with Moegi?

200
00:11:59,266 --> 00:12:00,927
What am I going to do, you ask?

201
00:12:02,603 --> 00:12:03,695
You want to know?

202
00:12:04,138 --> 00:12:04,729
Wha?!

203
00:12:04,939 --> 00:12:05,871
Don't move!

204
00:12:05,940 --> 00:12:07,669
If you do,
the brat's dead meat!

205
00:12:08,275 --> 00:12:11,711
Y-You. Why're you doing this?!

206
00:12:11,912 --> 00:12:13,971
I want the first Hokage's
Scroll of Sealing!

207
00:12:14,148 --> 00:12:16,139
If you bring it to me,
I'll return the brat!

208
00:12:17,184 --> 00:12:18,811
Scroll of Sealing...

209
00:12:21,155 --> 00:12:21,985
Umm...

210
00:12:22,890 --> 00:12:23,948
Sasuke...

211
00:12:24,692 --> 00:12:25,852
What's up, all of a sudden?

212
00:12:26,794 --> 00:12:27,761
Sakura...

213
00:12:28,495 --> 00:12:32,261
Give up on the Chunin Exam...
It's too early for you.

214
00:12:33,601 --> 00:12:34,568
Is it...?

215
00:12:34,869 --> 00:12:35,426
I thought so...

216
00:12:36,737 --> 00:12:38,932
The Chunin Exam is
a gathering of top dogs...

217
00:12:39,707 --> 00:12:42,198
You might die if you're not careful...

218
00:12:43,177 --> 00:12:44,371
Sasuke...

219
00:12:44,445 --> 00:12:46,845
So you're worried about me, right?

220
00:12:47,081 --> 00:12:48,878
Yeah... kind of...

221
00:12:50,718 --> 00:12:52,652
What a display of affection, eh?

222
00:12:52,720 --> 00:12:54,847
Get lost! If you don't want to die.

223
00:12:54,955 --> 00:12:56,946
Don't talk as if you know everything!

224
00:12:59,326 --> 00:13:00,850
Don't make me angry!

225
00:13:00,961 --> 00:13:01,791
Sasuke!

226
00:13:04,298 --> 00:13:05,060
Don't take me lightly!

227
00:13:10,437 --> 00:13:11,233
Sasuke!

228
00:13:25,185 --> 00:13:26,277
Sasuke?

229
00:13:27,488 --> 00:13:28,318
Sasuke!

230
00:13:28,455 --> 00:13:30,047
Sasuke!!

231
00:13:33,928 --> 00:13:35,225
What're you doing?

232
00:13:35,296 --> 00:13:37,059
Hurry up and bring me
the Scroll of Sealing!

233
00:13:37,298 --> 00:13:40,597
What'll happen... if I say, heck no?

234
00:13:40,901 --> 00:13:43,426
You don't care what happens
to this brat?

235
00:13:43,504 --> 00:13:47,838
Heh, I'm fine with whatever happens
to that bunch of straw, I say.

236
00:13:47,908 --> 00:13:50,069
Wha?!
When did he do that?!

237
00:13:52,613 --> 00:13:55,309
I've taken Moegi back from you,
thank you!

238
00:13:55,382 --> 00:13:58,112
As expected great leader!
Moegi respects you.

239
00:13:58,485 --> 00:14:01,352
Darn it! The Clone Jutsu, huh?

240
00:14:01,588 --> 00:14:03,749
You don't know when to give up!

241
00:14:07,695 --> 00:14:08,923
Naruto!

242
00:14:09,530 --> 00:14:11,589
Hey! You're late, Konohamaru!

243
00:14:11,865 --> 00:14:14,356
Konohamaru, I was scared.

244
00:14:14,435 --> 00:14:16,767
Oh, there there...

245
00:14:16,837 --> 00:14:18,327
Leader, did you catch him?

246
00:14:20,507 --> 00:14:22,270
Yup, as you can see!

247
00:14:22,576 --> 00:14:23,508
Huh? What?!

248
00:14:23,811 --> 00:14:26,075
Oh, it's the Substitution Jutsu!

249
00:14:26,146 --> 00:14:28,137
Dang it! When did he switch?!

250
00:14:28,816 --> 00:14:30,044
I see...

251
00:14:35,923 --> 00:14:37,322
If you don't want to turn out
like this,

252
00:14:37,391 --> 00:14:40,053
you'll give up on
the Chunin Exam, too.

253
00:14:40,661 --> 00:14:43,095
Sasuke, don't die...!

254
00:14:43,664 --> 00:14:46,292
Big mistake if you think
I'd say that.

255
00:14:46,734 --> 00:14:48,895
I was aware of this Genjutsu
right from the start!

256
00:14:49,136 --> 00:14:49,932
What?!

257
00:14:50,537 --> 00:14:52,437
The real Sasuke wouldn't do
something like

258
00:14:52,506 --> 00:14:54,701
invite me to go for a walk!

259
00:14:55,509 --> 00:14:56,840
Don't make me say
such frustrating things!

260
00:14:57,678 --> 00:15:01,045
That kind of elementary Genjutsu
won't work on me!

261
00:15:01,815 --> 00:15:03,146
Did you say elementary?

262
00:15:03,751 --> 00:15:04,479
That's right!

263
00:15:04,618 --> 00:15:07,143
Incidentally, I've seen through that
you're also an illusion

264
00:15:07,221 --> 00:15:09,746
and aren't really here!

265
00:15:11,492 --> 00:15:12,686
I don't know about...

266
00:15:12,760 --> 00:15:13,454
that!

267
00:15:19,466 --> 00:15:20,433
See?

268
00:15:22,569 --> 00:15:24,264
Just what I'd expect of
Kakashi's subordinate.

269
00:15:24,705 --> 00:15:27,538
However, this will become reality
in the Chunin Exam!

270
00:15:28,142 --> 00:15:30,167
I wonder if you can endure that...?

271
00:15:30,544 --> 00:15:33,638
I'm not scared!
I'll take them on anytime!

272
00:15:34,715 --> 00:15:38,048
The Chunin Exam isn't...
The Chunin Exam isn't...!

273
00:15:39,486 --> 00:15:41,545
I'm still not sure if I can do it...

274
00:15:49,663 --> 00:15:51,290
<i>That was a stupid thing to do...</i>

275
00:15:59,540 --> 00:16:00,734
How was it?

276
00:16:01,175 --> 00:16:03,439
We went to the trouble of having
a special preliminary exam,

277
00:16:03,644 --> 00:16:07,080
but all nine of the rookies passed.

278
00:16:08,749 --> 00:16:13,186
As you say, it appears their skills
have definitely improved.

279
00:16:13,821 --> 00:16:19,259
Well, the actual Chunin Exam
won't just end at this, but...

280
00:16:21,462 --> 00:16:22,588
Hey, have you heard?

281
00:16:22,963 --> 00:16:24,430
Rookies are going to be
in the Chunin Exam

282
00:16:24,498 --> 00:16:26,523
for the first time in five years.

283
00:16:26,967 --> 00:16:28,298
No way.

284
00:16:28,669 --> 00:16:31,604
It's probably just a Jonin battle of wills
or something anyway.

285
00:16:32,406 --> 00:16:33,168
No...

286
00:16:33,540 --> 00:16:37,067
The story is that three among them
are that Kakashi's unit.

287
00:16:37,511 --> 00:16:39,240
That's interesting...

288
00:16:39,646 --> 00:16:41,546
Well, be that as it may...

289
00:16:43,851 --> 00:16:45,682
That's a sad story...

290
00:16:49,523 --> 00:16:52,151
Sakura, you're late!

291
00:16:52,860 --> 00:16:54,919
Yeah... sorry...

292
00:17:01,835 --> 00:17:03,803
Morning, Sasuke.

293
00:17:04,304 --> 00:17:05,032
Yeah...

294
00:17:06,306 --> 00:17:08,934
<i>Something's strange about Sakura.</i>

295
00:17:15,916 --> 00:17:18,316
So, are you sure you're going
to attempt taking

296
00:17:18,385 --> 00:17:19,875
the Chunin Exam with that skill?

297
00:17:19,953 --> 00:17:22,649
May it'd be best if you runts quit.

298
00:17:22,789 --> 00:17:25,223
You're green assed brats, after all.

299
00:17:26,393 --> 00:17:28,884
Please let us through.

300
00:17:33,967 --> 00:17:34,899
That's... mean...

301
00:17:36,336 --> 00:17:37,496
What did you say?!

302
00:17:37,838 --> 00:17:41,171
Listen!
We're being nice to you!

303
00:17:41,375 --> 00:17:43,468
The Chunin Exam is a high hurdle.

304
00:17:44,044 --> 00:17:46,410
Many times have we seen
people quit Shinobi

305
00:17:46,480 --> 00:17:49,574
as well as people who were
disabled for life

306
00:17:49,650 --> 00:17:52,050
just because they took this Exam.

307
00:17:52,553 --> 00:17:56,114
Also, a Chunin is at the level
of a unit leader.

308
00:17:56,323 --> 00:17:58,450
Mission failures,
death of subordinates,

309
00:17:58,525 --> 00:18:00,789
it's all part of the
responsibilities of a leader!

310
00:18:00,861 --> 00:18:02,886
A brat such as this a Chunin?

311
00:18:04,531 --> 00:18:08,467
What's so bad about weeding out
those who won't pass anyway?!

312
00:18:09,169 --> 00:18:10,500
A just argument.

313
00:18:10,837 --> 00:18:13,305
However, you will let me through.

314
00:18:14,908 --> 00:18:18,867
And could you also immediately
undo this barrier created with Genjutsu?

315
00:18:19,546 --> 00:18:21,514
I have business on the third floor.

316
00:18:22,416 --> 00:18:23,644
What's this guy talking about...?

317
00:18:24,051 --> 00:18:25,075
I don't know...

318
00:18:25,586 --> 00:18:28,453
- Well, well...
- So you noticed, eh?

319
00:18:29,957 --> 00:18:31,219
How about it, Sakura?

320
00:18:31,458 --> 00:18:33,790
You should've been
the first one to realize it.

321
00:18:33,961 --> 00:18:34,586
Huh?

322
00:18:34,761 --> 00:18:37,195
Your analytical strength and
Genjutsu know how

323
00:18:37,264 --> 00:18:40,392
has improved the most in our squad, so...

324
00:18:40,934 --> 00:18:42,128
Sasuke...

325
00:18:43,870 --> 00:18:44,837
Thank you...

326
00:18:45,672 --> 00:18:48,368
Of course. I realized it ages ago!

327
00:18:48,609 --> 00:18:50,509
You see, this is the second floor!

328
00:18:50,811 --> 00:18:51,505
Yup!

329
00:18:54,514 --> 00:18:59,076
Well, not bad...
But all you've done is to catch on.

330
00:19:00,187 --> 00:19:00,846
Right?!

331
00:19:11,732 --> 00:19:12,528
<i>H-He's fast!</i>

332
00:19:12,966 --> 00:19:13,990
This person...

333
00:19:14,067 --> 00:19:16,865
He's a different person from
when he was getting punched before!

334
00:19:18,639 --> 00:19:20,163
<i>He stopped my kick...</i>

335
00:19:20,240 --> 00:19:22,401
<i>What's with that Chakra in his arm?</i>

336
00:19:23,110 --> 00:19:25,510
Hey, this isn't what you promised.

337
00:19:25,846 --> 00:19:27,245
You were the one who said

338
00:19:27,314 --> 00:19:29,942
you didn't want to carelessly
attract attention and be watched.

339
00:19:30,250 --> 00:19:31,114
But...

340
00:19:32,152 --> 00:19:34,643
Oh boy...
This again...

341
00:19:35,889 --> 00:19:36,651
<i>This guy...</i>

342
00:19:37,658 --> 00:19:39,626
<i>The marks where he was hit</i>
<i>are disappearing.</i>

343
00:19:40,294 --> 00:19:41,226
<i>Was he faking?</i>

344
00:19:44,498 --> 00:19:48,025
My name's Rock Lee.
Your name's Sakura, right...?

345
00:19:49,102 --> 00:19:49,693
Huh?

346
00:19:51,038 --> 00:19:55,031
Please go out with me!
I'll protect you until I die!

347
00:19:57,311 --> 00:19:59,142
Absolutely... not.

348
00:20:00,614 --> 00:20:01,444
Huh?

349
00:20:02,983 --> 00:20:04,644
You're... too intense.

350
00:20:07,321 --> 00:20:09,050
Hey, you there.

351
00:20:09,856 --> 00:20:10,481
Identify yourself.

352
00:20:12,826 --> 00:20:14,088
<i>Dang it! Again?</i>

353
00:20:14,161 --> 00:20:15,788
<i>It's always about Sasuke!</i>

354
00:20:16,263 --> 00:20:19,494
When asking someone his name,
give your own name first.

355
00:20:19,900 --> 00:20:23,336
You're... a rookie, right?
How old are you?

356
00:20:24,237 --> 00:20:25,795
I'm not obliged to answer.

357
00:20:26,406 --> 00:20:27,304
What...?

358
00:20:28,909 --> 00:20:29,841
<i>Cute.</i>

359
00:20:35,082 --> 00:20:36,071
Too intense, huh...

360
00:20:37,818 --> 00:20:39,285
Uninterested, huh...

361
00:20:40,520 --> 00:20:43,648
Now then!
Sasuke, Naruto, let's go!

362
00:20:45,225 --> 00:20:48,558
So those are Kakashi and
Guy's treasured brats.

363
00:20:49,196 --> 00:20:52,632
Well, for the time being,
their applications will pass.

364
00:20:53,100 --> 00:20:53,896
Yeah...

365
00:20:55,869 --> 00:20:58,736
It appears this year's test takers
will be amusing...

366
00:20:59,773 --> 00:21:02,105
For us proctors too, eh.

367
00:21:05,078 --> 00:21:06,306
<i>Good grief...</i>

368
00:21:06,680 --> 00:21:10,446
<i>This Chunin Exam...</i>
<i>is full of monsters.</i>

369
00:22:52,355 --> 00:22:55,324
Bowl-cut, fuzzy eyelashes
and bushy eyebrows.

370
00:22:55,392 --> 00:22:56,654
Oh! It's you!

371
00:22:56,726 --> 00:22:59,217
You're the overly intense guy
who just got rejected by Sakura.

372
00:22:59,296 --> 00:23:01,423
What's with your bizarre
green jumpsuit?

373
00:23:01,698 --> 00:23:04,997
What? You want to challenge me,
bushy browed bumpkin?

374
00:23:05,335 --> 00:23:08,930
I'll teach you that it's a million years
too soon to be doing that.

375
00:23:09,573 --> 00:23:13,805
Next episode:
"Chunin Challenge: Rock Lee vs. Sasuke!"

376
00:23:13,877 --> 00:23:16,641
As for me,
I'm going to kick butt once again!
